Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 751 Filed 08/10/22 Page 211 of 261 1372
LC6VMAX6 Maguire - direct
1 MR. EVERDELL: No objection.
2 THE COURT: 904-R is admitted. You may publish.
3 (Government's Exhibit 904-R received in evidence)
4 BY MS. MOE:
5 Q. Looking at Government Exhibit 904-R, and in the foreground, is that the same massage table we were just discussing?
6 A. Yes, ma'am, it is.
7 Q. Directing your attention to the far left doorway we see here in this photograph, where did that doorway lead?
8 A. That doorway leads to an adjoining bathroom.
9 MS. MOE: Ms. Drescher, if you could please take this exhibit down and show just the witness, the Court, and counsel what's been marked for identification as Government Exhibit 917-R.
10 Q. What is this exhibit?
11 A. This again is in this massage room. This is also taken from a different angle, with the focal point being the massage table in the center of the photograph.
12 Q. Is this a fair and accurate depiction of a separate angle of the interior of the massage room?
13 A. Yes, ma'am.
14 MS. MOE: Your Honor, the government offers Government Exhibit 917-R.
15 MR. EVERDELL: No objection.
16 THE COURT: 917-R is admitted. You may publish.
17 SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300
18 DOJ-OGR-00012962
